				<td colspan="2"><span>At 65 people beg me to PL their alts (and their own AA's) by swarming the nightstalkers in plane of nightmare. If you're going to AA at 65, PoN seems to be the place.
<br />
Frankly, I hate swarm kiting. Its a horrid bore, and the exp you get in groups once you can hit BoT, Sol Ro, and elemental planes is just fine with me.
<br />
Don't know what level you are right now, Planett but the truth is you are capeable of getting a full AA every 45 minutes at level 65 by going solo. In a group setting, you can get an AA just about every 1.25 hours, depending on where you hunt - if your guild isn't up to speed on PoP flags, hard LDoNs are solid exp in a full 65 group. Thats my experience anyway.</span></td>
