				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">An aa in 45 minutes in PoN swarming? That seems pretty fast for me. I have tried hobgoblins and gargoyles and it usually take an hour and 20 minutes or so per aa. </span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />

<br />
It's definitely doable. I've done an AA in 40-45 mins easily at hobgoblins. Gather 9 hobgoblins and as many wraiths as you can find and begin swarm. Add the horse you can target from ledge above and when the swarm starts getting smaller, add in vexed banshees (or are you afraid of getting summoned a couple of times<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-7.gif" border="0" alt="Perplexed" hspace="2" /> )
<br />

<br />
By the time you clear out a few banshees and the horsie, some of the hobs and wraiths will have respawned...go grab em and begin the fun all over again.
<br />

<br />
Very easy to get an AA in 45 mins here...I've been doing it almost every night for the past 3 months while I'm LFG.
